Merge pull request #33 from kevinhughes27/cv_mist_issues

Mist Issues

Fix Broken Purchase Promise

When I refactored this I broke it so it returned immediately.

Now it's good again.

Disable Buttons on Loading

On the non-testrpc systems things take time.
This makes it better.

Fix Mist Async Issues

Mist requires you to give a callback when getting accounts, so I moved
it into a helper and refactored a couple promises to make everything
work out.
